parameters: Looks like we made it in time.
Did you have a way to escape from the prison?

But it's not a problem. The preparations for the
ritual are complete.
There's no way I'll let you do that.

Are you planning to fight me? You were supposed to
obediently stay captured before.

The situation is completely different. I have
enough magical power.
So what? Our talents are different from yours.

Besides, I don't think just three people can take
on us.

(It's okay... Except for Jackson, they shouldn't
be a big deal)

Did you call for help? Hehe, it seems like the
teachers are busy dealing with the higher-ups.

There's no one to interrupt. Let's take our time
and deal with them.
You are... a member of the student council.

Do you think the student council can just enter
the Magic Research Club room without permission?

I didn't come here as a member of the student
council.
Why on earth are you here...

I was also investigating about the Magic Research
Club.

I didn't intend to come out, but if it's going to
be like this, then the situation is different.

Since it seems like I can expose the misdeeds of
the Magic Research Club, I will also assist
Masamune and the others.

I don't really understand, but if you're willing
to help, I welcome it.
They all just barge in without permission.
I'll take them all down at once!

I will take care of the executives. Is it alright
if I leave Jackson as the representative?
But are you okay by yourself?

No problem. I'm not a member of the student
council for nothing.
It's still daytime... but please, Sayoko.
Are you satisfied with this world?

It would be good to have a little talk before we
fight.

So, what's the deal with this narrow-minded world
of wizards?

Of course. Even though we use magic, we are also
fighting demons for the sake of humanity.
That's right. I have the same opinion.
Then why do you summon demons?

We need a strong power that can rival both demons
and heroes or the church.
The magic we use is just imitation.

Have you ever seen true magic used by demons with
ranks?

Magic that is different from just offensive magic
or healing magic, magic that can change the world.

And I will show you how to correct this twisted
world.

To achieve that, making a contract with a demon is
the quickest way.
Your way of doing things is wrong.

Those who deny magic are not enemies. If you make
a contract, you will become a demon.
I don't mind. If it helps me achieve my goal.

I'm different from those who just complain without
doing anything.

I know I don't have as much talent as Senior
Jackson, but I have to stop it.

Elena understands better than anyone how dangerous
summoning demons can be.

That's because it was summoned by someone with
little magical power. I can control it.

But you've never had experience fighting a real
demon, right?
What do you plan to do if it doesn't go well?

If I can't even control a single demon, then I
won't be able to change the world.
I don't care about what happens after I fail.
This is a troublesome situation, isn't it?
Enough talk. I will stop your plan.

(Once I achieve my goal, I will defeat Leviathan
too)

(We're only cooperating out of mutual interest, so
it's natural for us to be enemies)
Oh, so Amelia is going to fight too?
I thought for sure you would side with us.
That's right. Why would Amelia side with you?

What's wrong? Don't you want to be honest with me
like you were before?
Masamune, you don't have to listen.

(Why are you so impatient... No, there's no need
to think about that)

It's pitiful to be killed by me without knowing
anything.

I'll tell you everything. While you were
desperately trying to defeat me, Amelia was
fucking around.

Blowjobs were amazing. At first, it was awkward,
but once I taught her, she quickly became skilled.

I think she cried the first time we had sex. Well,
it couldn't be helped since it was an orgy with
creampie.
But don't worry. She said it felt good in the end.

Don't lie to me like that. We even took a bath
together. That time, I fucked her in the ass.
You're trying to shake me up completely...
Then show your boobs to that guy.

There's no way she would have nipple piercings
that I gave her as a present, right?

I haven't heard a word of what that person said.
I'll defeat them quickly.
Thank you for believing in me.

But... there's something we need to talk about
once it's over.
Ah, I'll listen to anything once it's over.
But no matter what happens, I will protect Amelia.
I can only afford to be relaxed for now!

„ÄêMasamune„ÄëI managed to come back somehow, but next
time I'll win.
